<HEADLINE> Jackie Gleason Statue Unveiled in NY  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Even Ralph Kramden would have been hard-pressed
to dream up a self-aggrandizing scheme to top this: an 8-foot
bronze statue of the bus driver in front of the Port Authority Bus
Terminal.
</P>
<P>
   The half-ton likeness of Jackie Gleason's character in ''The
Honeymooners'' was unveiled Monday.
</P>
<P>
