<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-28 22:27 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> American woman wins new trial in Peru, life sentence voided  </HEADLINE>
By RICK VECCHIO
<TEXT>
<P>
   LIMA, Peru (AP) - More than four years after hooded military
judges convicted American Lori Berenson of planning a rebel attack
